<section class="section"><div class="container"><div class="mission-grid">
  <div class="mission-content"><p class="eyebrow">Our Story</p><h2>We Transform Your Finances</h2><p>We are two siblings from Nicaragua who immigrated to the United States over 20 years ago, looking for better opportunities, as many of us have done when leaving our home country.</p><p><strong>Jeziel Guzmán</strong>, Certified Public Accountant (CPA), and <strong>Siny Guzmán</strong>, Software Engineer, joined our professional knowledge to create a company based on real values, honest work and total transparency.</p><p>We know firsthand the challenges the Latino community faces in the USA. That is why our goal is to offer real help, with clear information, no lies, no tricks and no fine print.</p><p>We do not just work with numbers or technology. <strong>We work with people.</strong></p><a href="/en/free-consultation" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:20px;">Schedule Your Appointment Today</a></div>
  <div class="mission-image"><img src="/assets/team.webp" alt="Guzman Tax Team" loading="lazy"/></div>
</div></div></section>
